<h1>Bonjour<%= " #{@user.email}" if @user&.email %> 👋</h1>

<p>Click the button below to sign in to Plume. The link expires in 15 minutes and can only be used once.</p>

<p><a href="<%= @url %>" style="background:#0a7; color:#fff; padding:12px 20px; border-radius:6px; text-decoration:none;">Sign in to Plume</a></p>

<p>If the button does not work, copy and paste this URL:</p>
<p><%= @url %></p>

<p>If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
